<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 28, 1994, Wednesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 2; Column 3; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
