<P>
BIG WEST CONFERENCE HONORS UCI'S SIMMONS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By JOHN WEYLER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 UC Irvine freshman Kevin Simmons was named Big West player of the week 
Tuesday.Simmons, a 6-foot-9 forward, totaled 31 points and 21 rebounds and made 
13 of 24 field-goal attempts in two Irvine victories last week. 
</P>
