Oregon State, 89-73, and scored 14 points with 10 rebounds in Saturday night's 
69-66 victory over St. Mary's. 
</P>
<P>
 Simmons is third on the team in scoring, averaging 10.6 points and is second 
in rebounding (8.1). JOHN WEYLER 
