<P>
COMMUNITY COLLEGE ROUNDUP; MURDENT SCORES 35 AS GOLDEN WEST BEATS PHOENIX 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Julie Murdent scored a career-high 35 points as Golden West beat Phoenix, 
96-64, in the opening round of the Fullerton women's basketball tournament 
Tuesday at Fullerton College. 
</P>
<P>
 Murdent, a sophomore forward from Fountain Valley High, was 15 of 22 from the 
field and five of nine from the free-throw line.She also had 13 rebounds. 
</P>
<P>
