College of the Canyons at 8:45 tonight. 
</P>
<P>
 In another tournament game: 
</P>
<P>
 Fullerton 57, L.A. Pierce 41 -- Fullerton fell behind, 11-0, but rallied to 
lead at the half, 29-16. Christa McDonald had 16 points and 11 rebounds for the 
Hornets (8-8) who play Long Beach at 7 p.m. in the quarterfinal round. 
