<P>
 Harold Krensky, 82, a former president of Federated Department Stores and a 
trustee of Boston University for 30 years. Krensky joined New York-based 
Bloomingdale's in 1947 and worked there until 1960, when he became an executive 
vice president at Filene's in Boston.In 1963, he became president and chief 
