<DOCNO> LA122894-0091 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 111940 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
December 28, 1994, Wednesday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 1; Column 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
