SUSPECTED GANG MEMBERS SOUGHT IN BEATING OF TEEN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Police were seeking four to five suspected gang members who severely beat a 
14-year-old La Palma boy Tuesday. 
</P>
<P>
 The boy, who was not identified, was in serious condition with head injuries 
at UCI Medical Center in Orange after being kicked and beaten with fists and 
bottles near Windsong Avenue and Bellhaven Street, said Sgt. Jeff Kirkpatrick. 
</P>
