 Police found the boy unconscious and convulsing on the sidewalk shortly before 
4 p.m., Kirkpatrick said. 
</P>
<P>
 The suspects -- described by police only as teen-age Asian boys -- fled in a 
light blue Honda Civic, Kirkpatrick said. He said they shouted the name of a 
gang based in Buena Park and Cerritos as they beat the boy. 
</P>
<P>
 Anyone with information on the beating was asked to call police at (714) 
523-4552. 
