<P>
HAWKINS SPEARHEADS ALL-DIVISION IX TEAM; HIGH SCHOOL FOOTBALL: NORDHOFF BACK 
NAMED SEGMENT'S PLAYER OF YEAR AFTER RUSHING FOR REGION-HIGH 2,454 YARDS. 
