FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A public art piece protesting the San Joaquin Hills Toll Road, cited in 
Tuesday's Calendar for its effectiveness, was called "The Witness Box." An 
incorrect title was given. 
</P>
</TEXT>
